::Feline::

She looked at K-9, "Would you like to take in a chamber as well, it 
might make you feel better." she said in a soft voice and gave him a 
warm smile.

She turned and walked over to the counter and picked up a small 
transwelder,(like a soldering iron)  and walked over to HotRod's CR. 
She looked in through the window to  check on him. She looked down 
and shook her head. "I just hope there will be enough of him left for 
me to put back together.  I've never lost a bot before, but,"she said 
with concern and worry.  She looked up at K-9,"I'll do my best for 
him." she said with a soft smile.
